twoStepLoginConfirmation.message: Avtentikacija v dveh korakih dodatno varuje vaš račun, saj zahteva, da vsakokratno prijavo potrdite z drugo napravo, kot je varnostni ključ, aplikacija za preverjanje pristnosti, SMS, telefonski klic ali e-pošta. Avtentikacijo v dveh korakih lahko omogočite v spletnem trezorju bitwarden.com. Ali želite spletno stran obiskati sedaj?

uncheckIfPublicDevice.message: Uncheck if using a public device

unlockMethodNeededToChangeTimeoutActionD.message: Set up an unlock method to change your vault timeout action.

updateKey.message: To funkcijo lahko uporabite šele, ko posodobite svoj šifrirni ključ.

updateMasterPasswordWarning.message: Your master password was recently changed by an administrator in your organization. In order to access the vault, you must update it now. Proceeding will log you out of your current session, requiring you to log back in. Active sessions on other devices may continue to remain active for up to one hour.

updateWeakMasterPasswordWarning.message: Your master password does not meet one or more of your organization policies. In order to access the vault, you must update your master password now. Proceeding will log you out of your current session, requiring you to log back in. Active sessions on other devices may continue to remain active for up to one hour.

uriPosition.description: A listing of URIs. Ex: URI 1, URI 2, URI 3, etc.

useAnotherTwoStepMethod.message: Uporabi drugi način prijave v dveh korakih

valueCopied.description: Value has been copied to the clipboard.

vaultTimeout.message: Zakleni trezor, ko preteče toliko časa:

vaultTimeoutActionPolicyInEffect.message: Your organization policies have set your vault timeout action to $ACTION$.

vaultTimeoutLogOutConfirmation.message: Logging out will remove all access to your vault and requires online authentication after the timeout period. Are you sure you want to use this setting?

vaultTimeoutPolicyInEffect.message: Your organization policies have set your maximum allowed vault timeout to $HOURS$ hour(s) and $MINUTES$ minute(s).

vaultTimeoutPolicyWithActionInEffect.message: Your organization policies are affecting your vault timeout. Maximum allowed vault timeout is $HOURS$ hour(s) and $MINUTES$ minute(s). Your vault timeout action is set to $ACTION$.

vaultTimeoutTooLarge.message: Your vault timeout exceeds the restrictions set by your organization.

warning.description: WARNING (should stay in capitalized letters if the language permits)

weak.description: ex. A weak password. Scale: Weak -> Good -> Strong

weakAndBreachedMasterPasswordDesc.message: Weak password identified and found in a data breach. Use a strong and unique password to protect your account. Are you sure you want to use this password?

weakMasterPasswordDesc.message: Glavno geslo, ki ste ga izbrali, je šibko. Za primerno zaščito svojega Bitwarden računa morate uporabiti močno glavno geslo. Ste prepričani, da želite uporabiti izbrano glavno geslo?

webAuthnDesc.message: Use any WebAuthn compatible security key to access your account.

webAuthnNewTab.message: To start the WebAuthn 2FA verification. Click the button below to open a new tab and follow the instructions provided in the new tab.

youWillBeNotifiedOnceApproved.message: You will be notified once approved.

yourAccountsFingerprint.description: A 'fingerprint phrase' is a unique word phrase (similar to a passphrase) that a user can use to authenticate their public key with another user, for the purposes of sharing.

yourVaultIsLocked.message: Vaš trezor je zaklenjen. Za nadaljevanje potrdite svojo identiteto.

yubiKeyDesc.message: Za dostop do svojega računa uporabite YubiKey. Podprti so YubiKey 4, 4 Nano, 4C in naprave NEO.

yubiKeyTitle.message: Varnostni ključ YubiKey za enkratna gesla
